“This is my first time of watching this festival. I am overwhelmed by the range of events. It’s impossible to watch all that I want to”Vandana, student,Thiruvananthapuram“I am at work till 7 p.m., but have come to watch programmes on all days, not just today for Oppana. It is the vibrancy and energy of Oppana that I like.”P. Harikumar,entrepreneur at Technopark“We came fourth in the Arabanamuttu competition in the higher secondary school category last year. We hope to better our performance in Thiruvananthapuram. The students have been training hard for the past few months.”Shareef, teacher, GovernmentVHSS, Kathirur